perilhfqh/setai ku/klw| to\ trape/zion dei/xeis</G> [<G>ou(/tws</G>] <G>dixotomh/sas ta\s tou= trapezi/ou
gwni/as</G> (&lsquo;Now, that the trapezium can be comprehended in a circle you
